OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny patchy mist and fog quickly
OL,6,Fclearing first thing. Otherwise
OL,7,Flargely dry with sunny spells with the
OL,8,Fodd light shower not to be ruled out.
OL,9,FTurning increasingly cloudier through
OL,10,Fthe afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy evening with rain
OL,13,Fspreading across from the west. Rain
OL,14,Fwill continue through the rest of the
OL,15,Fnight, with occasional heavy bursts in
OL,16,Fthe early hours.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
