OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FEarly rain across northern
OL,6,Fareas will quickly clear. Then bright
OL,7,Fspells and frequent showers for the
OL,8,Frest of the day, some likely heavy and
OL,9,Fthundery in the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FVariable amounts of cloud with showers
OL,13,For a few spells of rain. Often rather
OL,14,Fwarm in any sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
